description: Show cscotun0 IP address on GNOME panel. Do not show loopback addresses (127.0.0.0/8) or other network interface IP addresses. Please install moreutils package as a dependency. Forked from https://github.com/AdamantisSpinae/gnome-extension-tun0-ip-address and modified tunnel interface it looks at.
name: cscotun0 IP Address
